## Client Libraries

### Python

```python
from replit import db

# Set
db["key"] = "value"
db["user"] = {"name": "Diego", "role": "admin"}

# Get
print(db["key"])         # → value
print(db["user"]["name"])  # → Diego

# Delete
del db["key"]

# List keys
print(list(db.keys()))

# Prefix search
matches = db.prefix("user")
```

### Node.js

```javascript
const Database = require("@replit/database");
const db = new Database();

// Set
await db.set("key", "value");
await db.set("user", { name: "Diego", role: "admin" });

// Get
const val = await db.get("key");       // → "value"
const user = await db.get("user");     // → { name: "Diego", role: "admin" }

// Delete
await db.delete("key");

// List keys
const allKeys = await db.list();
const filtered = await db.list("user"); // prefix search

// Get all
const everything = await db.getAll();
```

Install: `npm install @replit/database`

### Go

```go
import "github.com/replit/database-go"

db, _ := database.New()

// Set
db.Set("key", "value")

// Get
val, _ := db.Get("key")

// Delete
db.Delete("key")

// List
keys, _ := db.List("prefix")
```

